Illusion (Glamer)Level: Magic1, Sor/Wiz 1Components:  V,S,FCasting Time: 1 actionRange: TouchTarget: Object touched weighing up to 5lb./levelDuration: 1day/levelSaving Throw: None (seetext)Spell Resistance: NoThis spell allows the caster to mask a magic item's aurafrom detection. If the object bearing undetectable aura hasidentify cast on it or is similarly examined, the examinerrecognizes that the aura is false and detectsthe object's actualqualities if he succeeds at a Will save.